\c 15
\s Imilayo mayelana leminikelo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo\x + 15.18. Levi 23.10. Dute. 7.1.\x*: Lapho lifika elizweni lokuhlala kwenu, engilinika lona,
\v 3 lisenza umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, umnikelo wokutshiswa kumbe umhlatshelo\x + Levi 1.2,3.\x*, owokugcwalisa isithembiso, loba emnikelweni wesihle\x + Levi 7.16; 22.18,21.\x*, loba emikhosini yenu emisiweyo\x + Levi 23.8,12,36; Nani 28.19. Dute. 16.10.\x*, ukwenza uqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, okuvela enkomeni kumbe ezimvini\x + Gen. 8.21. Eks. 29.18. Levi 4.31; Nani 28.27; 29.2,8,13.\x*,
\v 4 lowo-ke onikelayo umnikelo wakhe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Levi 2.1; 6.14.\x* uzasondeza umnikelo wokudla, ube ngokwetshumi lempuphu ecolekileyo\x + Eks. 29.40. Levi 23.13.\x* ixubene lengxenye yesine \w yehini\w** yamafutha\x + Levi 14.10; Nani 28.5.\x*;
\v 5 lewayini libe ngumnikelo wokunathwayo, ingxenye yesine \w yehini\w**, uzakulungisa lomnikelo wokutshiswa loba umhlatshelo, owewundlu elilodwa\x + 28.7,14.\x*.
\v 6 Kumbe owenqama lizalungisa umnikelo wokudla, ube zingxenye ezimbili etshumini zempuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, ingxenye yesithathu \w yehini\w**\x + 28.12,14.\x*;
\v 7 lewayini libe ngumnikelo wokunathwayo, ingxenye yesithathu \w yehini\w**, uzalinikela libe liphunga elimnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 8 Njalo nxa lilungisa ithole eliduna lenkomo libe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa kumbe umhlatshelo, owokugcwalisa isithembiso, kumbe iminikelo yokuthula eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Levi 7.11.\x*,
\v 9 uzanikelela-ke ithole lenkomo umnikelo wokudla, ube zingxenye ezintathu etshumini lempuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, ingxenye \w yehini\w**\x + 28.12,14.\x*.
\v 10 Linikele iwayini libe ngumnikelo wokunathwayo, ingxenye yehini, kube ngumnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo olephunga elimnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 11 Kuzakwenziwa njalo ngaleyonkunzi, loba ngaleyonqama, loba ngewundlu, kumbe ngezinyane\x + Nani 28.\x*.
\v 12 Njengenani elizalilungisa, lizakwenza njalo kuleyo laleyo, ngokwenani lazo.
\v 13 Wonke owokuzalwa elizweni uzazenza njalo lezizinto, ekunikeleni umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo woqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 14 Uba-ke owemzini ohlala njengowezizwe lani, kumbe loba ngubani ophakathi kwenu ezizukulwaneni zenu, njalo enikela umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo woqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, njengoba lisenza uzakwenza njalo.
\v 15 Kuzakuba lesimiso sinye kini abebandla lakowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe\x + Eks. 12.49. Nani 9.14. 15.29,30.\x*, isimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu; njengani uzakuba njalo owemzini phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Levi 3.17.\x*\nd*.
\v 16 Kuzakuba lomthetho munye lesimiso sinye kini lakowemzini ohlala lani njengowezizwe.
\p
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 18 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Ekungeneni kwenu elizweni engilisa kulo\x + 15.2. Dute. 26.1.\x*,
\v 19 kuzakuthi nxa lisidla okokudla kwelizwe, linikele umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Josh. 5.11,12.\x*.
\v 20 Ngokokuqala kwenhlama yenu\x + 15.21. Neh. 10.37. Hez. 44.30.\x* lizanikela iqebelengwana\x + Dute. 26.2,10.\x*, kube ngumnikelo wokuphakanyiswa\x + Levi 2.14; 23.10-17.\x*; njengomnikelo wokuphakanyiswa webala lokubhulela, ngokunjalo lizawuphakamisa.
\v 21 Ngokokuqala kwenhlama yenu\x + 15.21. Neh. 10.37. Hez. 44.30.\x* lizanika eN\nd kosi\nd*ni umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa ezizukulwaneni zenu.
\p
\v 22 Uba-ke liduha, lingenzanga yonke imilayo le iN\nd kosi\nd* eyikhulume kuMozisi\x + Levi 4.2.\x*,
\v 23 konke iN\nd kosi\nd* elilaye khona ngesandla sikaMozisi kusukela ngosuku iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalaya ngalo kusiya phambili ezizukulwaneni zenu,
\v 24 kuzakuthi-ke uba kwenziwe ngokungazi, kungekho emehlweni enhlangano, inhlangano yonke izanikela ijongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo, libe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa, kube luqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lomnikelo walo wokudla, lomnikelo walo wokunathwayo njengomthetho\x + 15.8-10.\x*, lezinyane lembuzi elilodwa, libe ngumnikelo wesono\x + Levi 4.23; Nani 28.15.\x*.
\v 25 Umpristi uzakwenzela-ke inhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli inhlawulo yokuthula, bakuthethelelwe, ngoba kuyikungazi, futhi bona bazaletha umnikelo wabo, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, lomnikelo wabo wesono phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, ngenxa yesiphambeko sokungazi kwabo\x + Levi 4.20.\x*.
\v 26 Lenhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli izakuthethelelwa, lowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwabo, ngoba kubo bonke abantu kwakusekungazini.
\p
\v 27 Uba-ke umuntu oyedwa esona ngokungazi, uzasondeza isibhuzikazi esilomnyaka owodwa, sibe ngumnikelo wesono\x + Levi 4.27,28.\x*.
\v 28 Lompristi uzawenzela lowomphefumulo owone ngokungazi inhlawulo yokuthula, lapho one ngokungazi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, ukumenzela inhlawulo yokuthula; uzakuthethelelwa-ke\x + Levi 4.35.\x*.
\v 29 Lizakuba lomlayo munye kwalowo owona ngokungazi, owokuzalwa elizweni phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, lowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwabo\x + 15.15.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Kodwa umuntu okwenza ngabomo, engowokuzalwa elizweni loba engowemzini\x + Dute. 17.12. Hlab. 19.13. Heb. 10.26.\x*, ethuka iN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 44.16.\x*\nd*; njalo lowomuntu uzaqunywa asuke phakathi kwabantu bakibo\x + 15.31. Eks. 30.33.\x*.
\v 31 Ngoba edelele ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, wephula umlayo wayo, lowomuntu uzaqunywa lokuqunywa; ububi bakhe buzakuba phezu kwakhe\x + 2 Sam. 12.9. 2 Lan. 36.16. Zaga 13.13.\x*.
\s Ukubulawa komuntu othile owatheza inkuni ngesabatha
\p
\v 32 Kwathi abantwana bakoIsrayeli besenkangala, bafica umuntu etheza inkuni ngosuku lwesabatha\x + Eks. 35.3; 20.8.\x*.
\v 33 Labo abamficayo etheza inkuni bamletha kuMozisi lakuAroni lakunhlangano yonke.
\v 34 Bamfaka esitokisini, ngoba kwakunga\add ka\add*tshiwo ukuthi kuzakwenziwani kuye\x + Levi 24.12.\x*.
\v 35 IN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 31.14,15.\x* yasisithi kuMozisi: Lowomuntu kabulawe lokubulawa; inhlangano yonke izamkhanda ngamatshe ngaphandle kwenkamba\x + Levi 24.14-16. 1 Kho. 21.13. Seb. 7.58.\x*.
\v 36 Lenhlangano yonke yamkhuphela ngaphandle kwenkamba, yamkhanda ngamatshe waze wafa, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\s Mayelana lentshaka zezembatho zabantu
\p
\v 37 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 38 Khuluma ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, ubatshele ukuthi bazenzele izintshaka emagumbini ezembatho zabo, ezizukulwaneni zabo, lokuthi bafake entshakeni yomphetho intambo eluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + Dute. 22.12. Mat. 23.5.\x*.
\v 39 Njalo kuzakuba kini yintshaka ukuze likukhangele, likhumbule yonke imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, liyenze, lingadingi lilandele inhliziyo yenu lilandele amehlo enu\x + Hez. 6.9.\x*, eliphinga ngokukulandela\x + Hlab. 73.27; 106.39.\x*.
\v 40 Ukuze likhumbule lenze yonke imilayo yami, libe ngcwele kuNkulunkulu wenu\x + Levi 11.44,45.\x*.
\v 41 NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu eyalikhupha elizweni leGibhithe ukuba nguNkulunkulu wenu; ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Levi 22.33.\x*.
